name: T3ZO GIRLS//Shinryaku
description:
Hey, buddies! Well, i would like to introduce to you the ''T3ZO G1RLS'' PROJECT! This is my first great project here in the Nft community, and i really hope you enjoy it!

Well, first of all, Cyberpunk is my favorite fiction genre, so this is the base to all of the project. Shinryaku means agression, she is the Tezo Lady V.0.1! 

Each Tezo Lady will represent a single feeling/emotion, so here is Shinryaku for all of you! What emotion do you want to see next? If you guys enjoy and wanna see more or give me cool ideas for the project, you can follow me on Twitter and send me a dm!

I would be very grateful if you guys could support my work helping me to share this amazing project or adding it to your collections!

I aprecciate you for taking a little bit of your time until here, hope you guys are all alright, see ya! <3
